---
title: Double  Spiced Chicken & Oregano Roast Veggie Toss with Pickled Onion & Mayo
description: Chicken and veggies, it’s a staple go-to for any dinner. Tonight we're going to mix it up! Cooking the chicken in our
Aussie spice blend gives it an additional burst of flavour, then smoothed over with a roast veggie toss dressed with
Parmesan cheese and oregano.
